Joseph Olaoluwa the sole distributor of Suzuki vehicles in Nigeria, CFAO Motors, has unveiled a special COVID Business Support package for Suzuki vehicles to all corporate organisations in any part of the country. In a press statement emailed to our correspondent, the motoring brand said it has placed a N1m discount on some models of Suzuki vehicles from August 15 to September 30. General Manager, CFAO Motors, Mrs Aissatou Diouf, was quoted to have said, “This package, which is aimed at providing succor to corporate organisations because of the negative effect on their businesses as a result of the COVID-19 pandemic, will offer N1m discount for some models of Suzuki vehicles within August 15 and September 30.” She said corporate organisations were entitled to the N1m discount when they purchase any of these Suzuki models – Alto, Dzire, or Ciaz within the given period. According to her, all the three models are suitable for corporate organisations as official vehicles for Executives or pool cars. Copyright PUNCH.
